Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.41,utwitter,,0,0,0,,虽说好像来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.41,utwitter,,0,0,0,,阿弘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.41,utwitter,,0,0,0,,今天的晚饭是肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.41,utwitter,,0,0,0,,阿弘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.41,utwitter,,0,0,0,,真的想把那家伙杀杀杀杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.41,utwitter,,0,0,0,,阿弘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.41,utwitter,,0,0,0,,已经忍不下去了 我要杀了他…
